<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Under Construction - Christ Centered Crafts</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          #40fad3 0%,
          #91bde4 33%,
          #d28df3 66%,
          #fd6efc 100%
        );
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .container {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 60px 40px;
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      .logo-container {
        width: 100%;
        height: 250px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .logo-container img {
        max-width: 100%;
        max-height: 100%;
        object-fit: contain;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .logo-placeholder {
        width: 150px;
        height: 150px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #40fad3 0%, #91bde4 33%, #d28df3 66%, #fd6efc 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 48px;
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(64, 250, 211, 0.4);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #40fad3 0%, #91bde4 33%, #d28df3 66%, #fd6efc 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .old-name {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #999;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-style: italic;
      }

      .message {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .features {
        text-align: left;
        margin: 30px 0;
        padding: 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          rgba(64, 250, 211, 0.15) 0%,
          rgba(145, 189, 228, 0.15) 33%,
          rgba(210, 141, 243, 0.15) 66%,
          rgba(253, 110, 252, 0.15) 100%
        );
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 2px solid rgba(64, 250, 211, 0.3);
      }

      .features h3 {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #40fad3 0%, #91bde4 33%, #d28df3 66%, #fd6efc 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .features ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .features li {
        padding: 8px 0;
        color: #555;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 25px;
      }

      .features li:before {
        content: "✓";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: #40fad3;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .contact-info {
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-top: 30px;
        border-top: 2px solid #eee;
      }

      .contact-info p {
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .contact-info a {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #40fad3 0%, #91bde4 33%, #d28df3 66%, #fd6efc 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .contact-info a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          padding: 40px 25px;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
          font-size: 1rem;
        }
      }

      em {
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 600;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #40fad3 0%, #91bde4 33%, #d28df3 66%, #fd6efc 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo-container">
        <img
          src="/Users/brianmoore/Documents/PersonalProjects/ChristCenteredCrafting/christ-centered-crafts2.PNG"
          alt="Christ Centered Crafts Logo"
        />
      </div>

      <p class="subtitle">We're Getting a Fresh New Look!</p>

      <p class="old-name">Formerly: Xpress Yourself Pro</p>

      <div class="message">
        <p>
          <h2>Exciting News!</h2> After much prayer and reflection, Xpress Yourself Pro
          is officially transforming into
          <em>Christ Centered Crafts!</em> This new name
          reflects the heart of my mission — to create meaningful,
          faith-inspired designs that uplift, encourage, and remind us of God’s
          presence in everyday life. Same creativity, same love, but now with a
          deeper purpose centered around Christ. Thank you for continuing this
          journey with me — your support means everything!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="features">
        <h3>What's Coming Soon</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Updated product collections</li>
          <li>Enhanced shopping experience</li>
          <li>Same great quality and service you love</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p><strong>Have questions?</strong></p>
        <p>Call me at 803-707-5667</p>
        <p>We'll be back soon with something amazing!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      // Optional: Add a simple animation on load
      document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        const container = document.querySelector(".container");
        container.style.opacity = "0";
        container.style.transform = "translateY(20px)";

        setTimeout(() => {
          container.style.transition = "all 0.6s ease";
          container.style.opacity = "1";
          container.style.transform = "translateY(0)";
        }, 100);
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
